0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px;\">\r\n				<tr class=\"crayon-row\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; background: 0px center; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; border: none !important; vertical-align: top !important;\">\r\n					<td class=\"crayon-nums \" data-settings=\"show\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline: 0px; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; vertical-align: top !important; background: rgb(223, 239, 255) !important; color: rgb(84, 153, 222) !important;\">\r\n						<div class=\"crayon-nums-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px center; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 15px !important;\">\r\n							<div class=\"crayon-num\" data-line=\"crayon-6091a2b5e6e95692186457-1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px center; font-size: inherit !important; font-family: inherit; text-align: center; height: inherit; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important;\">\r\n								1</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td class=\"crayon-code\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline: 0px; background: 0px center; width: 830.4px; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; vertical-align: top !important;\">\r\n						<div class=\"crayon-pre\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre; overflow: visible; tab-size: 4; border: none !important; background: none !important; line-height: 15px !important;\">\r\n							<div class=\"crayon-line\" id=\"crayon-6091a2b5e6e95692186457-1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px center; font-family: inherit; height: inherit; font-size: inherit !important; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important;\">\r\n								<span class=\"crayon-o\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font-size: inherit !important; font-family: inherit; height: inherit; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important; color: rgb(0, 111, 224) !important;\">&lt;</span><span class=\"crayon-e\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font-size: inherit !important; font-family: inherit; height: inherit; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important; color: rgb(0, 78, 208) !important;\">h1 </span><span class=\"crayon-t\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font-size: inherit !important; font-family: inherit; height: inherit; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important; color: rgb(128, 0, 128) !important;\">class</span><span class=\"crayon-h\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font-size: inherit !important; font-family: inherit; height: inherit; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important; color: rgb(0, 111, 224) !important;\"> </span><span class=\"crayon-o\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font-size: inherit !important; font-family: inherit; height: inherit; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important; color: rgb(0, 111, 224) !important;\">=</span><span class=\"crayon-h\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font-size: inherit !important; font-family: inherit; height: inherit; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important; color: rgb(0, 111, 224) !important;\"> </span><span class=\"crayon-s\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font-size: inherit !important; font-family: inherit; height: inherit; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important; color: rgb(0, 128, 0) !important;\">&quot;title&quot;</span><span class=\"crayon-o\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font-size: inherit !important; font-family: inherit; height: inherit; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important; color: rgb(0, 111, 224) !important;\">&gt;</span>Заголовок<span class=\"crayon-o\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font-size: inherit !important; font-family: inherit; height: inherit; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important; color: rgb(0, 111, 224) !important;\">&lt;</span><span class=\"crayon-o\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font-size: inherit !important; font-family: inherit; height: inherit; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important; color: rgb(0, 111, 224) !important;\">/</span><span class=\"crayon-v\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font-size: inherit !important; font-family: inherit; height: inherit; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important; color: rgb(0, 45, 122) !important;\">h1</span><span class=\"crayon-o\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font-size: inherit !important; font-family: inherit; height: inherit; line-height: inherit !important; font-weight: inherit !important; color: rgb(0, 111, 224) !important;\">&gt;</span></div>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n			</tbody>\r\n		</table>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(42, 55, 68); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(42, 55, 68); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n	Тут видно, что мы не просто написали &lt;h1&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;. В любой тег можно вписать дополнительные атрибуты. Они пишутся в открывающейся части элемента.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(42, 55, 68); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" class=\"aligncenter\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://webformyself.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/77/3.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(220, 220, 220); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(238, 243, 248); max-width: 94%; height: auto; display: block;\" title=\"\" width=\"700\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(42, 55, 68); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n	Сначала пишется имя самого атрибута, а потом задается его значение. В этом примере строчка class = &laquo;title&raquo; привяжет к нашему заголовку стилевой класс title, так что через него можно будет обратиться к этому элементу в css.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(42, 55, 68); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n	Между парными тегами мы записали то, что непосредственно будет выведено на экран. После этого следует закрыть тег. Если забыть это сделать, то это может привести к интересным ошибкам. Например, весь текст на странице может превратиться в заголовок. В одинарных тегах нельзя писать произвольный текст, в них можно задать только определенные атрибуты.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(42, 55, 68); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n	Любому html-элементу можно задавать какие-то атрибуты. Есть так называемые универсальные атрибуты, которые можно прописать любому элементу. К примеру, стилевой класс можно привязать к чему угодно. Также есть атрибуты, которые уникальны для каких-то тегов. Например:</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: 0px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(42, 55, 68); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"crayon-syntax crayon-theme-classic crayon-font-monaco crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate\" data-settings=\" minimize scroll-mouseover\" id=\"crayon-6091a2b5e6e9b132082352\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; padding: 0px; border-image: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: none; width: 850.763px; font-family: Monaco, MonacoRegular, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; color: rgb(42, 55, 68); height: auto; border-width: 1px !important; border-style: solid !important; border-color: rgb(153, 153, 153) !important; background: rgb(253, 253, 253) !important; overflow: hidden !important; position: relative !important; direction: ltr !important; text-shadow: none !important; line-height: 15px !important;\">\r\n	<div class=\"crayon-plain-wrap\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px center; margin: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; height: auto !important;\">\r\n		<textarea class=\"crayon-plain print-no\" data-settings=\"dblclick\" readonly=\"readonly\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 5px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; width: 848.763px; overflow: hidden; height: 14.4px; position: absolute; opacity: 0; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: no